ser_name":"金鹏","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1019485,"ip_address":"","ucode":"916180E1699264","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8e/5d/562e90d6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1510647595,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18690516779","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"    首先对新人来说，入职会安排导师，有新人邮件，包括日常规定、wiki、工具使用等，有问题可以和导师沟通。有助于快速熟悉进入状态。<br>    对于问题，有个万能句式“你觉的呢？”让大家明确责任，并在规定时间内讨论，然后约定下次讨论时间。从而培养大家都在动脑思考，做不同的方案，而不只是在问答的状态。","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":479,"user_name":"😺🤓😺","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1012858,"ip_address":"","ucode":"BBE313EE5AD213","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/74/7a/0dfb43f4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1510538942,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18690408126","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"以前我也是有问必答或者帮着找答案，直到自己也忙不过来了…… 后来索性只说自己大概猜测让别人去找问题和解决方案，结果证明小伙伴真的还挺值得培养…","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":478,"user_name":"禾子先生","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1004799,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7F637111BDC5C3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/54/ff/380eaec1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1510537940,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14395439828","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"工作了4年，期间也带过人，但思维模式都是帮忙找答案，今天这么一听，很是受用，谢谢","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":565,"user_name":"格非","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1004569,"ip_address":"","ucode":"89FABFFC377131","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/54/19/95ff4cbd.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1510827356,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10100761948","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"刚毕业入职一家小公司，没有leader带，出了问题就Google，再解决不了就只好问公司的一些老员工了，一般都是直接把你问题给解决了，问了几次为什么，人家都没说，稀里糊涂的就这样了","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":505,"user